{"tid":1952803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YG為旗下新女團註冊了商標 ∑(ﾟДﾟ)","createTime":"2020-03-31T23:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T12:19:41.000Z","uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b034b14bec847ea67164c7ee4057bf9f50625d1f","tid":1952803,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:01:36.000Z","msg":"YG Entertainment現正為推出新女團作最後準備，最近有網民於註冊專頁找到了有關新女團的商標；<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/01/064512_eb6e93ec2af1b7ed88ca03b4a2453a60.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F01%2F064512_eb6e93ec2af1b7ed88ca03b4a2453a60.jpeg&h=5540cb21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 分別為「BAEMON」和「Baby Monsters」。（圖／翻攝自商標註冊專頁）<br />\n<br />\n據小道消息，新女團將會以類似TWICE的可愛風格出道。<br />\n<br />\n四年前師姐BLACKPINK強勢出道，活動期間以總共13首歌拿下各個音樂節目一位、橫掃音源排行榜。到底師妹團「BM」出道又會帶來一波怎樣的熱度呢？"},{"pid":"a5ca1401fe2b71caf195d936fe117a1a067a6b13","tid":1952803,"uid":165368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:33:22.000Z","msg":"2月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1591b8c66e78ba94190621ef54d12b04ade4ca49","tid":1952803,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ca1401fe2b71caf195d936fe117a1a067a6b13","tid":1952803,"uid":165368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:33:22.000Z","msg":"2月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"下=="},{"pid":"8c119f857e44d7f604d37f9a206d234323196648","tid":1952803,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:47:27.000Z","msg":"其他成員solo 石沉大海"},{"pid":"3201ec5d54c0c25f859b9757ffe8ba30a1a3893a","tid":1952803,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c119f857e44d7f604d37f9a206d234323196648","tid":1952803,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03